He That Believeth


Verse 1:
He that believeth,
He that believeth,
Has everlasting life!
He that believeth
On the Father and the Son
Has Everlasting life!

Verse 2:
When I get to Heaven
I'm going to march all around-
Have everlasting life!
I'm going to sit by my Saviour
And put on my crown-
Have everlasting life!